&quot;);continue; /* 进入循环的下一轮迭代 */&#125;&#125;roll = roll_n_dice(dice, sides);printf(&quot;You have rolled a %d using %d %d-sided dice.
&quot;,roll, dice, sides);printf(&quot;How many sides? Enter 0 to stop.
